Fernando Torres' move to AC Milan is making the headlines in Italy as Chelsea have agreed to loan the Spanish striker out to the San Siro outfit.

La Gazzetta dello Sport go with the headline 'Torres Yes' as the Italians celebrate the arrival of Torres on their shores.

Torres is expected to earn in the region of €4million per season and will undergo a medical on Saturday, according to the Italian newspaper.

